# Mobius_Coder -- Project Brief

## What this is
Mobius_Coder is a Progressive Web App (PWA) designed as a focused coding assistant, an alternative to desktop AI applications for code generation, debugging, and review. It leverages a Vercel serverless backend, Supabase for data persistence, and a vanilla JavaScript frontend, routing queries to various cloud and local AI models.

## Current focus
The current development focus is on finalising the branding by incorporating new logo assets and updating all relevant HTML and manifest file references within the project.

## Key constraints
- Do not write or modify files without explicit user approval.
- Propose changes before writing, ensuring they are the simplest solution fitting existing code logic.
- Write clean, well-commented, production-ready code in British English.
- Debug systematically, explaining reasoning, and never truncating code.
- Avoid em dashes in PowerShell/batch files; use plain hyphens.

